SELECT
DATE(EVENT_TIMESTAMP)
AS EVENT_DATE,
COUNT(*) AS TOTAL_EVENTS,
COUNT(DISTINCT USER_ID)
AS UNIQUE_USERS
FROM RAW_EVENTS
GROUP BY DATE(EVENT_TIMESTAMP)
ORDER BY EVENT_DATE DESC;
